## Frequently Asked Questions

**How do I enhance a photo?**
Open Krispr, tap the **+** button, choose a photo from your library or take one with your camera, and Krispr's AI will enhance and colorize it automatically. Drag the before/after slider to compare, then save or share the result.

**How many free enhancements do I get?**
Free accounts include a limited number of enhancements. For unlimited enhancements, subscribe to **Krispr Pro** (monthly or yearly).

**How do I manage or cancel my subscription?**
Subscriptions are billed through your Apple ID. To manage or cancel, open **Settings → [your name] → Subscriptions** on your iPhone, or go to **Settings → Apple ID → Subscriptions**. Deleting the app does not cancel a subscription.

**How do I restore a purchase?**
On the Krispr paywall screen, tap **Restore Purchases**.

**How do I delete my account?**
In the app, go to **Profile → Delete Account**. This permanently deletes your account and associated data.

